The paper discusses neural network methods for open-domain question answering, which falls under the intersection of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of reinforcement learning (RL) in the proposed method also suggests a potential connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
